results.description: This flower was interesting because I couldn’t tell if this plant was alive or dead, but regardless it was gorgeous. Like the purple flower I photographed earlier, the plant itself was very unsteady, while the seeds or flower buds were not falling off, regardless of the winds pressure. I once again did not see any pollinators going towards it, however I suppose that could be from the somewhat sharp look the seeds or flowers have.
